{"tid":1389514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台發起不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-31T02:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T04:33:51.000Z","uid":275331,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0fc32fd3b15132a1640d7dff7256a425d363ab","tid":1389514,"uid":275331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbSmtNT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbSmtNT.png&h=d9d7d268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我最初都好支持天文台<br />\n但係8號風球真係影響到民生<br />\n依個行動對我黎講係絕對唔同意<br />\n依家公司準備趕我走<br />\n唔比我繼續開工<br />\n我要諗其他辦法偷偷地留係公司繼續開工<br />\n<br />\n垃圾天文台<br />\n你阻人番工，我仲要養妻活兒<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家一齊寫信投訴天文台"},{"pid":"ce03b34bc370e6006ba35f0d5c8837d3fcdf9950","tid":1389514,"uid":275331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dFT1tRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdFT1tRe.png&h=4daee5e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c655f71728b0cc066ffbdff9a5364dde12bdf2cd","tid":1389514,"uid":258646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"恥與為伍"},{"pid":"14176857d921bd2a817920f45542f05dba188ff9","tid":1389514,"uid":275331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172dfdd99dd161293b74297bde8656a44f4246c0","tid":1389514,"uid":275331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aef491a51138f3a2037163e21f0348e6659ba92","tid":1389514,"uid":275331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=